{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to cook up a storm in &quot;The Chef's Shift: First Course&quot; - a fast-paced typing game set in a bustling restaurant! With your keyboard as your weapon, you'll need to cook and serve delicious dishes to hungry customers before they lose their patience. But that's not all - you'll also need to juggle all kinds of crazy distractions, from rat invasions to unruly customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/extras/flag.png?t=1738942298\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a culinary journey through the Italian restaurant in The Chef's Shift: First Course, and experience the start of Lorenzo's chef career. Savor the diverse flavors of the cuisine, where each dish will feature different quirks &amp; challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/extras/whatoexpect.png?t=1738942298\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 1 teaspoon of <strong>chaotic, fast-paced</strong> gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 1 package of easy-to-pickup, hard-to-master <strong>TYPING</strong> mechanic </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 1 cup of fun <strong>time management</strong> bits </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/extras/typing.png?t=1738942298\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/extras/feats.gif?t=1738942298\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And we mean it! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Navigate through the menu by typing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Prepare &amp; serve your customers by typing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Select your dialogue choices by typing </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/extras/characters.png?t=1738942298\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/extras/cast.png?t=1738942298\" />Throughout the game, you will meet various characters, from customers with their own personality, to characters who propel the story forward. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/extras/wishlist.png?t=1738942298\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738942298","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738942298","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/6fc233781eeda175e269cd8070e4f3aaa6e8d775/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738942298","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516920/6fc233781eeda175e269cd8070e4f3aaa6e8d775/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738942298","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"The story is about mafia families and crime life. There will be frequent mention of criminal activity in the storyline like drugs, gang wars, illegal gambling etc.\r\nThe most violent thing shown is the display of gun and killing rats."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to cook up a storm in &quot;The Chef's Shift: First Course&quot; - a fast-paced typing game set in a bustling restaurant! With your keyboard as your weapon, you'll need to cook and serve delicious dishes to h